text: Dorian Hauterville (born 27 April 1990) is a French bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:French male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of France Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
